{"tid":1374863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫你地唔散，前掛散唔到？","createTime":"2019-07-28T01:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:42:53.000Z","uid":157228,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"636ba47733caf8d70d9fa2ab96b9b80f966aee84","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地老母<br />\n我重新一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有既去留喺由自己嘅意志決定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n下次邊撚個再講呢句 利用群眾壓力去令後排散水 我實屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n你可以做既喺同人講前線實際狀況（必須喺實際 唔好喺度鳩傳） 再叫人自己決定去留<br />\n<br />\n仲有果班屌7唔退阻住人退果班<br />\n唔該你地都反省下<br />\n有人要留守 你嘈咩？<br />\n<br />\n另外，喺度提醒勇武巴<br />\n如果後排比散水狗散水成功<br />\n請重新諗一次局勢 再決定自己行動"},{"pid":"6c6efd792b88efcdb3d732aba4576078c1d98d94","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"535daa64c89684aa2365ad79271f74b4227be7c4","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:58:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97049fec2bcf2f328a28433c1d5d68799def432b","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:58:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"379389b72d1bf0f49f1bb6c8453f1159fec6bf60","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:58:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"292e0008fc406aadc62e1344361c2f8d3e32df09","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:59:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fcdf727e60a576dda2bc84b0218635b1c442a3c","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"510e95c405a47d2f23be8f747164b7c005aacc35","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"268efc8af5a2c9aa6d36dc51a754d55810a0a580","tid":1374863,"uid":157228,"like":0,"